=head1 NAME

_BASELINE_INTERFEROGRAM_ - baselines the interferogram

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _BASELINE_INTERFEROGRAM_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive subtracts a baseline from the interferogram.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

None.

=head1 EXTERNAL TASKS

KAPPA.

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

None

=head1 OUTPUT FILES

None.

=head1 NOTES

None.

=head1 AUTHOR

Graham Bell E<lt>g.bell@jach.hawaii.eduE<gt>

